020-10-07T06:15:34.000Z","msg":"唉 就係對business world 冇咩興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNursing 好似有意義好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8f5e74bd582bddda697eff3ec874268a29e4b9","tid":2233391,"uid":32768,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"acdff51102c456aaac1353f965473c060eeed52e","tid":2233391,"uid":74022,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"67cc87af360f0122b6444b362a04b7396fb40cdd","tid":2233391,"uid":1484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:13:14.000Z","msg":"唔試下跳出inhouse dcm fund risk嗰啲先？正路人工高過nursing 如果stay 大4多三年更加唔洗講<br />\nnursing都幾多人話唔好做 跳出big4 已經輕鬆返好多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:15:34.000Z","msg":"唉 就係對business world 冇咩興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNursing 好似有意義好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:25:22.000Z","msg":"但好惡做呢<br />\n支持你轉行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你真係覺得做nurse好有意義 <br />\n<br />\n屋企人係醫院做 <br />\n本身好地地 做幾年變左隻喪屍咁 樣殘脾氣差<br />\n又日日受氣（女人多 事非多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a5b148c9364e83054a10bc0db2f373dcc2d706","tid":2233391,"uid":71893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"我都係讀business ，做左幾年bank,而家準備直接去澳洲讀nursing移民"},{"pid":"3a9bcfa331edc072122e59c6855e87e5ef4cf50f","tid":2233391,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32a5b148c9364e83054a10bc0db2f373dcc2d706","tid":2233391,"uid":71893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"我都係讀business ，做左幾年bank,而家準備直接去澳洲讀nursing移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"公開試讀phd Chen bio?<br />\n係咪一定要有理科底"},{"pid":"eba11f6df2e02debebafb69654da178ebecefe06","tid":2233391,"uid":237300,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"仲咁後生，無謂為咗嗰2年去繼續未來30年做咩，但你最好了解下nursing 做咩先，唔係又浪費多幾年時間，唔好咁心急同跟風"},{"pid":"20afad503ec592ad2f0d64648205732f22c49f93","tid":2233391,"uid":71893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a9bcfa331edc072122e59c6855e87e5ef4cf50f","tid":2233391,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32a5b148c9364e83054a10bc0db2f373dcc2d706","tid":2233391,"uid":71893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"我都係讀business ，做左幾年bank,而家準備直接去澳洲讀nursing移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"公開試讀phd Chen bio?<br />\n係咪一定要有理科底"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"無讀，唔一定，文科底都有學校收，我有朋友已經過左去讀"},{"pid":"a12d0a1c16a461aaa0d8fde57a23129c106477cd","tid":2233391,"uid":193205,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:45:26.000Z","msg":"巴打，咪撚咁睇唔開呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟都係濕尻bba grad, 做左一段時間hr 同local audit firm就走去讀nursing master 轉行，真係覺得自己做緊狗<br />\n<br />\n實習果陣，日日比班讀唔成書讀護士嘅老屎忽係度踩我地master 出身，話我地比錢就讀得，得knowledge 冇經驗。屌，成班讀唔成書嘅冇得揀唯有讀護士，就係度踩讀得成書嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屎尿血膿痰我都唔介意，但比呢班人踩真係唔gur 呀，你話冇錢就要頂姐，巴打你有專業資格就咪撚入火海啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔單止，係醫院做真係做狗，啲醫生態度差到可以你想像唔到，係station 大叫原子筆呢，跟住就有個護士死死地氣拎比佢，仲要死狗咁話x 醫生，原子筆呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連叫醫生英文名都比人話冇禮貌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有好多醫生冇禮貌到啲紙一疊掉比你，掉晒落地下，你自己慢慢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果刻我真係覺得自己係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴打你頂得順啲人事同性質就去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa2bff0eb253703fab632de90b1c741a4860b65","tid":2233391,"uid":58254,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:11:48.000Z","msg":"屌你牌都攞埋就繼續做啦，起馬人工唔差可以儲到錢<br />\n再讀多4,5年到時香港點都無人知，賺少4年真係搏唔過<br />\n咩興趣意義個d 就咪諗啦，護士大把野會搞到你覺得心灰意冷<br />\n<br />\n我呢d垃圾文科fg 無晒出路先逼住讀護士"},{"pid":"2c2a520122b8e8895dee9d70398bf8de58f4d205","tid":2233391,"uid":99644,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:33:48.000Z","msg":"樓主千其唔好讀，都係睇你際遇好唔好（唔好既居多），做護士真係可以做到尊嚴都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d151526eb0c2ca8c349aa7efb868c4ef6968538a","tid":2233391,"uid":89249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:38:03.000Z","msg":"自己計下數讀3年nursing賺少幾多（會計做多3年應該差唔多50k,護士起薪到時應該33左右），再問下身邊護士惡唔惡做，就可以衡量到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df7bcab78e388f73ad1a239cb8f1096a503dbee","tid":2233391,"uid":147031,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T20:27:55.000Z","msg":"兩邊都係火海 咁點解轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 護士背後係好辛苦 你想到40歲仲返shift 咩"},{"pid":"a0942288b813976cfd3cda0bf9de161566daa25b","tid":2233391,"uid":380046,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:35:22.000Z","msg":"做姑娘係好惡做，利申ha rn 想裸辭"},{"pid":"a0134b4f60d331bbc509c58fcdc9fc2de0e8cdd7","tid":2233391,"uid":93284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:08:38.000Z","msg":"女人做謢士都講到冇晒尊嚴咁，男人做咪仲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過算啦香港地打工不嬲都冇乜尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bfeecb89ccd11504ea55f3dad334b1f5ced7ff","tid":2233391,"uid":157487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"做咩護士 專心炒股啦"},{"pid":"6ac7843b25e1605d383939ec46c4c0f5fb795de1","tid":2233391,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r