":"同埋成日都講護士起薪雖然係比一般人高，但高出個d人工根本係比你睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打不如講下比樓主知，以你所知有幾多同事要睇精神科，腰同腳勞損或者生cancer個d<br />\n等樓主唔好入火海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af5c7884aa84663740a9447d1224b6c9792cf84","tid":2233391,"uid":193205,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3965b91a9d575c2db3a52feb2b017471a139135f","tid":2233391,"uid":208954,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6d76bf9315b14bb4847f988c935a523b5e12a8be","tid":2233391,"uid":193205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34d8a62f676cfa100b8716bad31f88e8d189cc60","tid":2233391,"uid":222728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:17:27.000Z","msg":"私家定公立呀巴打"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"公立呀，咪撚以為私家先係做狗啦。根本係公院都係做狗，服侍醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要啲senior 覺得護士對醫生恭敬係合理喎，縱到啲醫生咁無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未入行我都估唔到做到成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本私家同公院都係屎，或者ngo oah 好啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"我就真係笑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自問讀書真係唔叻，但有自知之明，所以先話自己係濕尻bba 出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至於果個咩master 我更加知係entry level 啦，唔通我又會好似班老屎忽咁拎黎j<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但果啲老屎忽係冇自知之明喎，以為自己真係咁叻，仲係度踩人喎，簡單英文都可以讀錯晒。其實讀書差去讀護士冇問題，但咪撚自我膨脹到咁啦, 仲要強調自己讀好多書，唔係pca 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知邊個先係白鴿眼呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀之前做research就緊啦，但唔通咁就唔怨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為錢入火海又唔怨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我只係講比樓主聽現實係點，咁都可以比人批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc74b132d6b5b50b7b07ee1499b7ccfc5fb46486","tid":2233391,"uid":71849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T15:49:32.000Z","msg":"真係唔建議<br />\n唔係一句話有意義就要去做<br />\n日日返shift 返到退休你想唔想？<br />\n返shift真係好難約人<br />\n到你想生小朋友 你又好難就時間陪佢<br />\n返工又多女人 好多閪人<br />\n日日都可以比說話你聽<br />\n轉工又難<br />\n<br />\n做返金融相關既工<br />\n出路闊好多<br />\n生活都正常好多"},{"pid":"e8c862ec7f3d29dbf749936dabff8560a7e2e0e3","tid":2233391,"uid":222728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d76bf9315b14bb4847f988c935a523b5e12a8be","tid":2233391,"uid":193205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34d8a62f676cfa100b8716bad31f88e8d189cc60","tid":2233391,"uid":222728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a12d0a1c16a461aaa0d8fde57a23129c106477cd","tid":2233391,"uid":193205,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:45:26.000Z","msg":"巴打，咪撚咁睇唔開呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟都係濕尻bba grad, 做左一段時間hr 同local audit firm就走去讀nursing master 轉行，真係覺得自己做緊狗<br />\n<br />\n實習果陣，日日比班讀唔成書讀護士嘅老屎忽係度踩我地master 出身，話我地比錢就讀得，得knowledge 冇經驗。屌，成班讀唔成書嘅冇得揀唯有讀護士，就係度踩讀得成書嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屎尿血膿痰我都唔介意，但比呢班人踩真係唔gur 呀，你話冇錢就要頂姐，巴打你有專業資格就咪撚入火海啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔單止，係醫院做真係做狗，啲醫生態度差到可以你想像唔到，係station 大叫原子筆呢，跟住就有個護士死死地氣拎比佢，仲要死狗咁話x 醫生，原子筆呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連叫醫生英文名都比人話冇禮貌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有好多醫生冇禮貌到啲紙一疊掉比你，掉晒落地下，你自己慢慢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果刻我真係覺得自己係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴打你頂得順啲人事同性質就去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:17:27.000Z","msg":"私家定公立呀巴打"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"公立呀，咪撚以為私家先係做狗啦。根本係公院都係做狗，服侍醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要啲senior 覺得護士對醫生恭敬係合理喎，縱到啲醫生咁無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未入行我都估唔到做到成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本私家同公院都係屎，或者ngo oah 好啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c638f52f152b70e9d4465ba99bfe847f0b1d6a","tid":2233391,"uid":185868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20afad503ec592ad2f0d64648205732f22c49f93","tid":2233391,"uid":71893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a9bcfa331edc072122e59c6855e87e5ef4cf50f","tid":2233391,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32a5b148c9364e83054a10bc0db2f373dcc2d706","tid":2233391,"uid":71893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"我都係讀business ，做左幾年bank,而家準備直接去澳洲讀nursing移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"公開試讀phd Chen bio?<br />\n係咪一定要有理科底"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"無讀，唔一定，文科底都有學校收，我有朋友已經過左去讀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:53:45.000Z","msg":"想問你地係揀讀2年graduate entry 定照入3年Bsc?"},{"pid":"2a0353865343557d9d2d1b8dc22fe04663c9f36c","tid":2233391,"uid":35271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"bba 唔可以移民咩"},{"pid":"6cf57e427ec1ea1071b649644900a09127ba6d3b","tid":2233391,"uid":35580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"唔好咁多幻想 乖乖地繼續做會計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"